sub_eq_top_iff:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr⊤» -/

@[simp]
theorem sub_eq_top_iff : ∀ {a b : WithTop α}, a - b = «expr⊤» ↔ a = «expr⊤» ∧ b ≠ «expr⊤»
  | _, «expr⊤» => by simp
  | «expr⊤», (b : α) => by simp
  | (a : α), (b : α) => by simp only [← coe_sub, coe_ne_top, false_and_iff]
#align sub_eq_top_iff sub_eq_top_iff

#print map_sub /-
theorem map_sub [Sub β] [Zero β] {f : α → β} (h : ∀ x y, f (x - y) = f x - f y) (h₀ : f 0 = 0) :
    ∀ x y : WithTop α, (x - y).map f = x.map f - y.map f
  | _, «expr⊤» => by simp only [h₀, sub_top, WithTop.map_zero, coe_zero, map_top]
  | «expr⊤», (x : α) => rfl
  | (x : α), (y : α) => by simp only [← coe_sub, map_coe, h]
#align map_sub map_sub
